divs: Sighting Detailsdriving down 75 saw a helicopter towards the south it moved east in a nice slow move like a helicopter. then it turned west and came back. when it got closer I se it wasn't a helicopter it was a big black object it pass over my van while I was driving down the road when it was straight over me I pulled over. I got to the back of the van it was cruising north west and I had a pair of binoculars the left eye piece was broke so I used the right side, is what I used to see it. it was smooth on top and had one red light on top and a bunch of white lights underneath.
